      "title": "Fragile Truth",
      "artist": "Beata Migas",
      "year": "2025",
      "description": "Dr. Johan Faber, a respected psychiatrist, is drawn into a chilling mind game with his enigmatic patient, Thomas. What begins as routine therapy spirals into a battle of wits as Thomas exposes Faber’s deepest fears and buried secrets. As reality blurs, Faber questions whether Thomas is truly a patient or a manifestation of his unraveling psyche. In a harrowing climax, he confronts the terrifying truth—his greatest enemy may be his own mind. Was anything ever real, or is truth just an illusion?",
