      "artist": "Ahmed Alameldeen",
      "year": "2025",
      "description": "In the sterile corridors of power, a high-level diplomat is haunted by surreal glitches as he prepares to cast a decisive veto against a life-saving ceasefire. His internal struggle is contrasted with the desperate, fragile hope of a humanitarian doctor in a war-torn refugee camp, whose world hangs in the balance. The film climaxes in the silent, tense chamber where a single word spoken becomes an act of immense violence, with immediate and tragic consequences.",
